%% Diagram: AbortSignal propagation through fetch and a stream pipeline
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor App
    participant Ctrl as AbortController
    participant Fetch as fetch
    participant Net as Network
    participant RS as response.body
    participant Pipe as pipeTo
    participant Sink as WritableStream

    App->>Ctrl: new AbortController
    App->>Fetch: fetch with signal
    Fetch->>Net: open connection
    App->>Pipe: pipeThrough then pipeTo with signal

    Note over Net,Sink: Data flows. User clicks cancel.
    App->>Ctrl: controller abort with reason
    Ctrl-->>Fetch: signal aborted = true
    Fetch-->>Net: terminate fetch and close socket
    Ctrl-->>RS: reader cancel with reason
    RS-->>Pipe: cancel propagates downstream
    Pipe-->>Sink: writer abort with reason
    Fetch-->>App: rejects with AbortError
